.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
\&\fINet::SSH::Perl::Cipher::DES\fR provides DES encryption
support for \fINet::SSH::Perl\fR. To do so it wraps around
\&\fICrypt::DES\fR, a C/XS implementation of the DES algorithm.
.PP
The DES algorithm used here is in CBC filter mode with a
key length of 8 bytes.
